## Definition of Done (Per Change)
- [ ] Scope completed
- [ ] Targeted tests updated or passing
- [ ] Worker packet and result packet filled for delegated work
- [ ] Touched Path IDs updated with smoke or contract coverage (Tier B/C)
- [ ] Verify gate passed
- [ ] Relevant docs updated
- [ ] Changelog updated
- [ ] Risks noted (or `None`)

## Required Handoff Format
- Files changed
- Commands or tests run with results
- Worker assumptions and blockers
- Open risks or follow-up refactors